00:04:20.170 --> 00:04:31.190
Shepherd right now in the oceans." But we
hate doing gloom speeches. We hate it when

00:04:31.190 --> 00:04:39.620
documentaries and stuff do that to us. We're
gonna lighten up on your lunch break. And

00:04:39.620 --> 00:04:47.730
so, we decided ultimately that we wanna talk
about--a lot of things that--a lot research

00:04:47.730 --> 00:04:56.030
data and our own personal experience out there
in the oceans, say that is the most important

00:04:56.030 --> 00:05:04.550
things that we could be doing right now. Now,
the thing is the, the first thing a lot, you

00:05:04.550 --> 00:05:13.150
might say, "Well, there's a whole lot of issues
out there like global warming or world hunger

00:05:13.150 --> 00:05:20.310
and cultural clashes," but the thing is, the
